# Definition API

MxF exposes handler registries through `MxFDefinitions`.

Register custom upgrade handlers:

```java
MxFDefinitions.registerUpgradeEffectHandler(effectHandler);
MxFDefinitions.registerUpgradeRequirementHandler(requirementHandler);
```

Register custom mission handlers:

```java
MxFDefinitions.registerMissionObjectiveHandler(objectiveHandler);
MxFDefinitions.registerMissionFilterHandler(filterHandler);
MxFDefinitions.registerMissionRewardHandler(rewardHandler);
```

Handlers validate YAML, parse typed model objects, and execute only their registered behavior. Do not pass raw YAML maps into gameplay services.
